---
title: Speedy Sesame-Teriyaki Ground Chicken Bowls with Carrots and Edamame Rice
description: This chicken teriyaki on pillowy jasmine rice hits all the right notes: salty, sweet, filling and as spicy as you like it! But the best part? It all comes together in just 25 minutes!
